The paper involves the creation of a 3D visual analysis platform for seabed data on smartphones, which involves visualization and analysis of integrated data. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) or Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the platform is designed for smartphones, which could suggest a focus on Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) or Cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the paper involves the use of WebVRGIS, which could suggest a focus on Information Retrieval (cs.IR) or Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). However, given the emphasis on 3D visualization and analysis, cs.GR and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
